OL,5, Martin Lewis has opened up about the   
OL,6, "horrendous" pressure he feels giving  
OL,7, advice on personal finance.            
OL,9,FThe financial journalist and "Money    
OL,10,FSaving Expert" told BBC Radio 4's the  
OL,11,FMedia Show he finds the stress "very   
OL,12,Fdifficult to manage".                  
OL,14,F"If somebody applies for this (benefit)
OL,15,Fand it stops another benefit, I        
OL,16,Fwouldn't sleep at night," he revealed. 
OL,18,FMr Lewis's MoneySavingExpert website   
OL,19,Fwas sold for #87m in 2012 and he hosts 
OL,20,F"The Martin Lewis Money Show" on ITV.  
